    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that can only be described as showroom-perfect. Every detail, from the lustrous exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled preservation. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of uncompromising quality, offering a driving experience that remains indistinguishable from its original delivery state. For the collector who accepts only the finest, this vehicle stands as a definitive benchmark.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
