      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a dual-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen boasts a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox with precise synchronizer engagement and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The chassis maintains its original lateral rigidity with refreshed OEM bushings and dampers. With flawless factory paint and an untouched interior, this vehicle offers the mechanical purity and tactile feedback required by the most discerning purist.",
